Reflection on 2022 // 

“A year of pruning and fine-tuning 
weeping and rejoicing 

strength conditioning 
and growing pains

to live is Christ, 
to die is gain

met by Gods grace
in the midst of failure

a deeper rooted trust 
in His faithfulness and character 

stripped of my hearts dreams 
and desires for the future 

a tireless tug-of-war 
with control and surrender 

owning what I can change
releasing what I can not

hope deferred and hope restored

for all You have given 
and taken away this year
I thank You, Lord. 

Here’s to joy in the journey 
of forever becoming 
more like Jesus.” // —mg

#morelikejesus #2022recap

march: madness indeed & loved every single moment 😂🫶🏼🏀

officially a HOMEOWNER, say what!?!🔑🍾🥳 A surreal moment that I have worked, prayed, planned and waited for for the past four years. Hard work pays off & God is faithful!!! I had written down in January a goal of buying my first home by the end* of 2023—never imagining a short 4 months later I’d be securing the condo of my freaking dreams!! God has blown me away in this process… all I can say is when something is meant for you, it will be! The doors will open, the right people will find you and things will flow effortlessly. I prayed for God to send the right people my way and man did He deliver. None of this would be possible without this incredible team by my side! 🙌🏼🙏🏼🔑

Special thanks to @caseywl @caseyandco for being the greatest realtor (who is now my friend & stuck with me for life💓🥹) and @brucesladick_mortgage for all your hard work in this process and to my parents who prayed alongside me daily, helping out in any and every way. I appreciate you all! #homeowner #smallbusinessowner #ephesians320

Wishing all you BHM LASH babes the happiest New Year and extending the biggest thank you for your support in 2023!!!🥂🥳 I want you to know I am filled with gratitude that I get to continue this dream job into year five. Without each one of you this business would not exist! I’m eager to see what the Lord has in store for 2024 as I take these next 21 days to pray, fast and recenter. 🙏🏼 I won’t be online much during this time but the studio will be up and running as usual. I’m looking forward to providing your beauty services this year! See you in the pink bungalow. 🌿💗 #lashartist #esthetician #smallbusinessowner
